  "texts": [
    "The same happened during the generation of the young adult novel (Table 1, Story 2).",
    "Apart from creating a distinctive concept, the chatbot easily incorporated new characters into the story (protagonist friend Liam and antagonist Dr Malloy).",
    "From the first attempt of generation, the character's portrait was not unique, but after asking additional questions, ChatGPT made it more original, adding drama to the plot and revealing the character from a different perspective.",
    "For example, after asking more questions about the antagonist's personality, it appeared that he once lost his beloved daughter, looking exactly like the main character, Elara, and this was one of the reasons for his antagonistic role in the novel.",
    "This plot twist was generated using additional questions and could hardly have been created by ChatGPT from simple generation."
  ]
}